{"tid":1694360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載]真。黃色經濟圈 想幫手足就入嚟望望","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T12:08:12.000Z","uid":199553,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdf5e4c5588cf24d2a28573545eb062bccc76f9","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"有關黃色經濟圈，一些難聽，卻又想講的話。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有接觸過前線，你會發現，塞錢援助，多少打擊了他們的自尊。<br />\n<br />\n有擋子彈的勇氣，卻不願向人求助。<br />\n<br />\n每次開口，都一定是窮途末路。所以，我從不Fact Check，你說一句就夠。<br />\n<br />\n這裡從來沒有美國錢，你還想他們證明什麼。<br />\n<br />\n很多老板和管理層，早在八月已著手籌備黃色經濟圈。<br />\n<br />\n在昨日，兩位家小店聯絡我，表明要出一分力請手足。原因，是看到將軍澳的新聞，久久無法入眠。<br />\n<br />\n尊嚴很重要。遇過一個，收到轉帳後打千字文回絕，轉頭就將錢捐去星火。<br />\n<br />\n他寧願捱壞，都不要無功受祿 &mdash; 即使，他已犧牲了這麼多。<br />\n<br />\n尊嚴很重要，單向的善意，是買一張贖罪券。<br />\n<br />\n現實層面，被捕者、入獄者、罪成者，尤其容顏曝光的，仕途一定有影響。<br />\n<br />\n除了堅持到底，重光前後的生活，都需要籌謀。<br />\n<br />\nTelegram有良心配對群組，其實不少商家已無名出力，幫得幾多就幾多。<br />\n<br />\n不能白白收你的錢，用工作來換，就是尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n所以，光時這一種概念的機構，我們要撐到底。摸索期總要學習，少一點譴責，多一點包容，讓市場共同成長。<br />\n<br />\n不同背景的手足都能養活自己，才是制度。<br />\n<br />\n中產或小商家，儲了點資本，捱得到，未餓死。為了他人準備，無必要，卻是避不過良心。<br />\n<br />\n因為抗爭而無法工作的人，很多。<br />\n<br />\n有人做執彈隊，手腳嚴重潰難。<br />\n有人做衝衝子，手掌肌肉裂開。<br />\n有人做急救員，精神創傷難治。<br />\n有女生做後援，長期黑M肚瀉。<br />\n<br />\n其中不少已經被捕，甚至確認控罪。將來的生活，除了贏輸，生活也是一個訴求。<br />\n<br />\n所以，再不現實，我們也需要黃色經濟圈。<br />\n￼<br />\n以下說話，很難聽。其實純黃的商圈，即使存在，規模都很小。要完全建立本土供需，把紅底或大陸成分去除，至少在供應層面就很難。<br />\n<br />\n何謂黃店，又要幾黃才算黃？深黃老板有一個淺藍員工，又要否杯葛呢？發展到一定程度的企業，就算持有人及高層再黃，公司都不會全部是手足。<br />\n<br />\n就算理想到，全公司都黃，上埋市都黃。鋪位業主一樣可以紅底，產品供應，多少都來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n界線難定，亦有黑心人開始抹黑，希望在良心經濟打擊對手。<br />\n<br />\n放棄潔癖，堅持幫襯。出名的要撐，不出名的，更加要撐。<br />\n<br />\n讓市場和標準自然調整，才會有出路。<br />\n<br />\n或者，不能黃到變金，但在可行的情況，保住黃店，才能保住手足。<br />\n<br />\n經濟不景，但很多自身難顧的生意人，仍然不斷開新Project，講明請學生和失業人士。<br />\n<br />\n顧客，多你一個就好多。人無完美，生意都一樣。如果做得不夠完善，請不要切割，不要負評。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭從來不會完結，制度要永恆監管，但至少要成長起來。正如我們都不要表面的和平，攬炒，是為了推倒重來。<br />\n<br />\n而重光的香港，也不能一日重整。<br />\n<br />\n政治需要過程，經濟都需要時間。在千萬無名英雄的生活裡，沒有光環，只要一點自尊。<br />\n<br />\n而你們堅持與包容，才能撐起一個新香港。<br />\n<br />\n黃店的認證，終究要市場自然調整。不是一個帖文或幾多正評，誰就可以黃到最後。<br />\n<br />\n不完美，可改善，但相信，我們會全盤接受。<br />\n<br />\n畢竟，無論哪個戰線，都比想像中漫長。<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈沒有約定的煲底，但希望我們的銀包，可以撐到底。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，共勉之。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 全力支持光時 - HKongs Mall，真黃店，沒有之一。<br />\nP.P.S. 黃店不一定會開名，有些「中立」商家，背後黃到發光。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Terry的媒體懶人堂<br />\n<br />\n全力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d57fa4b4c641fb312533448bb4c882a0c4ed818","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa68b19a4ff4ef70bfd7f80ffabd47bb460cd890","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5f4adefe3e05af537649d55108df1dfcc7b165","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6718aabf7cb1de66a98da1cb63051d3754d9c430","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d1cf234e475e3b16c3223bbc09b0f802bd8764d","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"881f66531aca87ac88c2079f26031b244faf6410","tid":1694360,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUmQwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUmQwH.png&h=4f6d902a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝祭 下午三點銅鑼灣見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1a6c3ed5b8eac43397f6ca5ed4e50e7b1a8c51c","tid":1694360,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f75b518407314cdd4b4579df857f7988b8b63a4","tid":1694360,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"有做實事支持場運動既一定有香港人支持<br />\n最驚係低調做，但做到自己生意都頂唔緊既店"},{"pid":"0d3f4ffd2736c60e1214fd6a413c1c47cd7b3615","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f75b518407314cdd4b4579df857f7988b8b63a4","tid":1694360,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"有做實事支持場運動既一定有香港人支持<br />\n最驚係低調做，但做到自己生意都頂唔緊既店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"呢啲知道要幫手推廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61aaf5ef7c6a4098baa9d9aff7deeed6e77f1707","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ade7ce55cc7564d9439ab56282150157314406b","tid":1694360,"uid":169836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11d5affca70d3fb7b10ca107a3b16fb939daa8de","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e53c85ef1b873f150969fc1dfb675184ffce6a","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cc2d10ec5623d71a0788b001e1e1ad85543259c","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afeb7f219a9fb1e18364ec3559a6c9453c98c79f","tid":1694360,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"最好係可以請返被捕而失去工作而手足"},{"pid":"e4b559b0e67a5668649f3836e5b6957cbed89d3c","tid":1694360,"uid":281401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"黃金經濟圈啊"},{"pid":"c2a320f9dcf4611998486b74450b28d4a169dc4f","tid":1694360,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"「出名的要撐，不出名的，更加要撐。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ncC7OR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ncC7OR.jpg&h=284ab9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">115全民V煞日目標範圍: 九龍西</span>"},{"pid":"78436732923381f06917717a276aa23d398d7295","tid":1694360,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c9fdf3f5d34944c25fded68cd7f60fc8abfb1d","tid":1694360,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"pusg."},{"pid":"5ef696554bb64d11e045ec5b4f0a107605b17e10","tid":1694360,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15b064441bc472d064fe20addca325e9434148d","tid":1694360,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"撐光時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca6a17a45c7b8907fc37be927760c05e06da9c6","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c1c1ea9724dcaaa6d9bc7fd88f176bbbd40956e","tid":1694360,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afeb7f219a9fb1e18364ec3559a6c9453c98c79f","tid":1694360,"uid":121